Encoding: UTF-8
Type: Package
Package: torino
Title: Reference-free Isoform Analysis via Empirical Bayes Poisson Matrix Factorization
Version: 0.1.0
Date: 2026-03-30
Authors@R: c(
    person("Cristian", "Buenabaden", role = c("aut", "cre")),
    person("Dongyue", "Xie", role = "aut", email = "dyxie@uchicago.edu",
           comment = "Author of bundled ebpmf.alpha code (https://github.com/DongyueXie/ebpmf.alpha)"))
Description: End-to-end pipeline for reference-free analysis of mRNA isoform
    variation in large-scale RNA-seq datasets. Includes functions for data
    preprocessing (column merging to reduce RAM usage, sample filtering) and
    Empirical Bayes Poisson Matrix Factorization. The EBPMF algorithm from the
    ebpmf.alpha package (Dongyue Xie) is bundled directly to simplify installation.
